title: Shelby Township- 2 Bed 3.5 Bath & Office Space Available Now!
posting_body: ['Now available is this beautiful and spacious 2-bedroom, 3.5-bath Live/Work Condo!', 'This property features an office/storefront space on the first level with a 1/2 bath for your employees and clients.', 'The upstairs portion of the unit features a spacious living room, two large bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and an additional 1/2 bath!', 'The property features a large standing shower, and appliances such as a refrigerator, stove, dishwasher, washer, and dryer.', 'Also, the unit includes a 1-car attached garage!', 'It is located on a quiet street in Shelby Township with easy access to restaurants and shopping.', 'Pets welcome.', 'Unit features:', '-Office/Storefront space', '-Spacious Living Room & Bedrooms', '-Large Stand-Up Shower', '-Appliances Include (Refrigerator, Stove, Dishwasher, Washer & Dryer)', '-Attached 1-Car Garage', 'Available Now!', '$1,995 Rent', '$2,900 Security Deposit', 'For more information or to schedule an appointment for a showing, please call', 'show contact info', '.', 'Thank you for your interest!', '*Please Note- Pet fee is an additional $40 per pet, per month.', 'Cities close by Rochester, Sterling Heights, Troy, Mount Clemens, and Auburn Hills.']
